name: THESINS//007 : FEAR
description:
ACT//007. ABANDONED HOUSE. 

“What is your biggest fear?” Asked Tom. “Rejection.” May answered. She lay her head over Tom’s shoulder. “What about you?”
Tom stubbed out his cigarette. “Ghost.” he chuckled as he kissed May.

Suddenly there was a loud knock on the door and someone barged in. May froze as she saw Tom got shot. Carl with gun in his hand, spring into a rage.
